content.query:
SELECT TOP (100) *
 FROM [s2_googleclassroom].[dbo].[courses] c
 LEFT JOIN [s2_googleclassroom].[dbo].[coursealiases] ca on ca.courseId = c.id
 LEFT JOIN [s2_googleclassroom].[dbo].[courseannouncements] can on can.courseId = c.id
 LEFT JOIN [s2_googleclassroom].[dbo].[courseteachers] ct on ct.courseId = c.id
 LEFT JOIN [s2_googleclassroom].[dbo].[users] ut on ut.userId = ct.userId
 LEFT JOIN [s2_googleclassroom].[dbo].[coursestudents] cs on cs.courseId = c.id
 LEFT JOIN [s2_googleclassroom].[dbo].[users] us on us.userId = cs.userId
